<div class="title">SpeedBalling, Sort Of</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines (Adderall) & Hydrocodone (Vicodin)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Sniper&Exact=1">Sniper</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Sniper. "SpeedBalling, Sort Of: An Experience with Amphetamines (Adderall) & Hydrocodone (Vicodin) (exp49766)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Apr 8, 2008. erowid.org/exp/49766</div>

